Nigel Stock (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nigel_Stock_(actor) 0 Nigel Hector Munro Stock (21 September 1919 – 23 June 1986) was an English actor of stage, screen, radio and television, who played character roles in many films and television dramas.
